---
import Layout from "@astro/layouts/Layout.astro";
import SimplePage from "@astro/components/SimplePage.astro";
---
<Layout title="Cookie Policy — PromptAndGo" description="What cookies we use and why.">
  <SimplePage title="Cookie Policy" updated="May 2026">
    <p>We use a small number of cookies to keep the site working and improve it.</p>
    <h2>Strictly necessary</h2>
    <p>Authentication, session, security tokens. Required — the service won't work without these.</p>
    <h2>Functionality</h2>
    <p>Theme preference (light/dark), saved filters, language preference.</p>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>Aggregated, privacy-respecting page-view stats. You can opt out from <a href="/account">account settings</a>.</p>
    <h2>Third parties</h2>
    <p>Stripe sets cookies during checkout; Supabase sets a session cookie for auth. We don't use advertising cookies.</p>
  </SimplePage>
</Layout>
